{"tid":510274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用《議事規則》敲花枱 梁耀忠要賠錢","createTime":"2017-12-26T09:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T16:02:30.000Z","uid":51904,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7de5603e7174d99a0615d0b6814d0b609d508ded","tid":510274,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T09:47:33.000Z","msg":"今個月十五號，《議事規則》修訂被強行通過。立法會「自閹」當日，有成十一個民主派議員被逐，當中梁耀忠、涂謹申同鄺俊宇被逐之前就企喺度，一邊大叫口號「反對修改《議事規則》」，一邊撕爛本《議事規則》，以示抗議， <br />\n<br />\n雖然最終佢哋三個被梁君彥再下令驅逐離開會議廳，但係相比被保安抬出去嘅朱凱迪同陳志全，佢哋都係被人半推行咁趕出去，唔算大動作。不過近日梁耀忠就因為當日嘅事，收到立法會秘書處嘅信。 <br />\n<br />\n原來佢當日用本差唔多兩吋厚嘅《議事規則》敲會議室張枱，因為《議事規則》係硬皮書，比一般精裝書仲要硬身，秘書處就出信被佢，話佢會議當日敲花咗張枱，佢哋會搵人嚟報價睇下整番要幾錢，當然就要梁耀忠埋單。"},{"pid":"e2fa7d73dc14ff12bde995542c8b7de95ef0fda7","tid":510274,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:36:37.000Z","msg":"扮少陣野啦"},{"pid":"797f9a5f992cfc709c89647ab24538253d9a2028","tid":510274,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T11:49:22.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"a78e8481a9a2a1847c728c77289b6805bb3b6eae","tid":510274,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:03:39.000Z","msg":"咁激進<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b3d2bc341e438384fada58c547b723036bbed1","tid":510274,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:06:11.000Z","msg":"柒頭仆街死"},{"pid":"32f36bb263ea3ca2253f399fc573089df8b961f6","tid":510274,"uid":30510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"死全家啦<br />\n誓估唔到中共有咁撚柒碌嘅臥底"},{"pid":"1cdc303311047bea31cdaa0cfa99bfa4ee90ab6f","tid":510274,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:12:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2016-2017年度立會傑出柒頭: 梁耀忠</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/456906/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/456906/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"ee3efd6aa90c8d02720b36e97d274e1c4a340e6b","tid":510274,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:13:46.000Z","msg":"好激進好暴力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533c3b3b0159c6454883569d0e828a17df5be136","tid":510274,"uid":71315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:44:55.000Z","msg":"哇好暴力"},{"pid":"a34e8ad986e6638dd3038f8a39956a129482b366","tid":510274,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:46:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我想反問返啲泛民打手</span><br />\n<br />\n1.點解梁耀忠要讓個主席位畀保蝗梁君彥呀？<br />\n2.點解2011年泛民要支持修改議事規則削自己權呀？<br />\n3.點解馮檢基要走去新西票令何君堯當選呀？<br />\n4.泛民爭取真普選個時間表係點呀？<br />\n5.點解陳志全玩鐵鍊就當抗爭呀？<br />\n6.點解雨革要預約被捕而唔係同政府談判呀？<br />\n7.點解要玩篤灰割席呀?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同我答撚哂佢呀打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"7242b1595cd9ad62703864a4daaf49431b763df4","tid":510274,"uid":118125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.kinliu.hk/upload/20161013/81b7f083b2ff7bc1f78001a1a82952c6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.kinliu.hk%2Fupload%2F20161013%2F81b7f083b2ff7bc1f78001a1a82952c6.gif&h=e9c1f7ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對唔住整花左張枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1455e6b3172836bc05bdc028b1f6ce8ba74963","tid":510274,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T16:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}